@@TJvMruList.AddData@Pointer@Integer
Description:
Use this method to add raw data in a MRU list containing raw data. The function returns true if the Value has been correctly added. if the MRU list contains strings, you have to call the Addstring method.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvMruList.AddString@string
Description:
Use this method to add a string in a MRU list containing strings. The function returns true if the Value has been correctly added. if the MRU list contains raw data, you have to call the AddData method.

