@@TJvMruList.EnumItems
Description:
Use this method to retrieve all the members of the MRU List. For each item of the list, the event OnEnumText or OnEnumData will be called. This function returns false if the MRU list is empty or inexistant.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvMruList.FindData@Pointer@Integer
Description:
Use this method to find a string in the MRU list. if the data asked has not been found or if the list is inexistant, the function will return -1.

Parameters:
Value: 
is a pointer to the data you are searching
Size:
is the size of the Value.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvMruList.FindString@string
Description:
Use this method to find a string in the MRU list. The strings are case sensitive. if the string asked has not been found or if the list is inexistant, the function will return -1.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvMruList.GetItem@Integer
Description:
Use this method to retrieve a specific element in the MRU list. The most recent one is at the Index 0, and the oldiest one is at the index GetItemsCount-1. if the index doesn't refer to a correct item, or if the list is inexistant, the function will return false.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvMruList.GetItemsCount
Description:
Use this method to get the number of elements in the MRU List. if the list is empty or inexistant, the function returns 0.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvMruList.GetMostRecentItem
Description:
Use this method to retrieve the most recent item. A call to this method is similar as the GetItem(0). It will retrieve the last item you have add to the MRU list and it will call either the OnEnumData or OnEnumText event. This function will return false if the MRU list is empty or inexistant.

